The project vision is for all Afghan girls, including the most marginalised, to be educated, equipped and supported with the knowledge, skills, and attitudes needed to help them interact effectively with the world and be contributing members to society. STAGES II will ensure continued access for current and new cohort girls to equitable, quality and protective education opportunities close to home.
